condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section I A | Description :The Project Implementing Entity shall vest FPTD with the overallmanagement of and coordination of Project implementation. | Due Date :04-Feb-2013

Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section I C | Description :The Project Implementing Entity shall, in carrying out the Project,implement the RAPs and the EMP, respectively, all in a manner and substance satisfactory to the Bank. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section II A | Description :The Project Implementing Entity shall monitor and evaluate the progressof the Project and prepare Project Reports in accordance with the provisions of Section 5.08 (b) of the General Conditions; andfurnish the semi-annual Project Reports to the Bank not later 45 days after the end of each reporting period. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section II B | Description :The Project Implementing Entity shall furnish the audited financialstatements to the Bank not later than six months after the end of each fiscal year of the Project Implementing Entity. | Frequency:Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section II B | Description :The Project Implementing Entity shall maintain a financial managementsystem and prepare financial statements in accordance with consistently applied accounting standards acceptable to the Bank. |Frequency :Yearly
